autocmd Filetype python nnoremap <F12> <Esc>:REPLDebugStopAtCurrentLine<Cr>
autocmd Filetype python nnoremap <F8> <Esc>:REPLPDBN<Cr>
autocmd Filetype python nnoremap <F7> <Esc>:REPLPDBS<Cr>
